HEADWORD: Fortunella
<hw>Fortunella</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>small genus of shrubs
called kumquats, native to South China, producing small ovoid orangelike
fruits called <prod>kumquats</prod>.</def>⟦br⟧
